### ============================================================
### STUDENT JOB APPLICATIONS API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### Login siswa dulu
# @name loginSiswa
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "siswa",
  "nisn": "0001234567",
  "school_origin": "SMA Negeri 1 Bogor",
  "unique_code": "BUDI0001234X9YZ"
}

###

### 1) CREATE DRAFT APPLICATION (UPLOAD CV)
POST {{baseUrl}}/student/job-applications
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="job_vacancy_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cover_letter"

Saya tertarik melamar posisi ini dan siap mengikuti proses seleksi.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cv"; filename="cv.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample-files/cv.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### 2) UPDATE DRAFT APPLICATION
@applicationId = 1
PUT {{baseUrl}}/student/job-applications/{{applicationId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cover_letter"

Saya memperbarui draft lamaran dan siap mengirim lamaran final.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### 3) SUBMIT DRAFT APPLICATION
POST {{baseUrl}}/student/job-applications/{{applicationId}}/submit
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### 4) LIST MY APPLICATIONS
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/job-applications
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}

###

### 5) SHOW MY APPLICATION DETAIL
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/job-applications/{{applicationId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSiswa.response.body.$.data.token}}
